{"tid":2448674,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳宗憲否認和周杰倫決裂！鬆口曝「師徒疏遠內幕」：他人生改變","createTime":"2021-03-16T05:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T06:07:12.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"50e151585913f5d9e10dd7940b764d2aa933eabc","tid":2448674,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:40:51.000Z","msg":"吳宗憲當年提拔周杰倫出道，雙方如今各自為綜藝天王、歌壇天王，但師徒之間卻幾乎零互動，兩人的私下恩怨更一直都是演藝圈的熱門話題，他近日上直播節目，再度談及和周杰倫的關係，他表示沒有決裂，更鬆口雙方之間疏遠的原因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5506/d5506861.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5506%2Fd5506861.jpg&h=372a4e64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲吳宗憲、周杰倫關係一直受到高度關注。（圖／翻攝自Facebook／吳宗憲、周杰倫）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吳宗憲近期上大陸直播，談及和周杰倫的恩怨時，他大讚周杰倫在自己心裡永遠都是一個天才、是一個鑽石，他表示兩人之間並沒有決裂，如果要追究疏遠的原因，他坦言：「如果真要說我們有什麼樣分叉的路的話，那也就是因為他人生有了不一樣的改變，他是一個從歌手變成一個巨星，變成一個世界級的巨星，他的生活裡面就慢慢去改變。」他更以湯姆克魯斯為例，「你不能期待湯姆克魯斯到現在還和高中老師有聯絡吧！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5506/5506862.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5506%2F5506862.jpg&h=b41b1403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5506/5506863.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5506%2F5506863.jpg&h=78b1149d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5506/5506863.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5506%2F5506863.jpg&h=78b1149d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5506/5506865.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5506%2F5506865.jpg&h=bede1d1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲吳宗憲否認與周杰倫決裂。（圖／翻攝自微博／飯圈雜談）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實上，吳宗憲和周杰倫是知名的「師徒關係」，周杰倫以前曾是吳宗憲的音樂助理，吳宗憲更一手栽培周杰倫出道，但兩人近年則幾乎沒有任何互動或合作，周杰倫2015年和昆凌舉辦婚禮時，也沒有邀請恩師吳宗憲，讓雙方不合傳言甚囂塵上，吳宗憲當時更不滿地表示：「漏掉我這封喜帖是不是太針對了？我是一排名字在那邊讓你打勾或打圈要不要邀請的人嗎？不發帖子是要給我難看囉！」周杰倫當時則表示沒邀請吳宗憲是媽媽葉惠美的決定。<br />\n<br />\n但吳宗憲2018年7月和「咻比嘟嘩」團員小鐘、小馬、劉畊宏在台北小巨蛋舉辦演唱會，周杰倫當時就在IG放上咻比嘟嘩的練團合照，並寫下：「演唱會加油啦！你們的合體又讓我彷彿回到過去，已經20年了，時間真快！」當時就盛傳兩人已經破冰。"},{"pid":"baa1eaf8ad1aa0379520625e1b43f771bb26e28c","tid":2448674,"uid":339805,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:42:22.000Z","msg":"樓豬大劣人黎，係咁po大陸新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc6cd4db1917b99262ad417225aee553e297e31","tid":2448674,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:42:35.000Z","msg":"講到口臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e07aee55f6083e3121166a0a5fbc763a902cfe6","tid":2448674,"uid":61271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:42:37.000Z","msg":"兩隻奶共狗"},{"pid":"598fa18dc12ba2f986eef1c2220421dac331e1c8","tid":2448674,"uid":172329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:42:55.000Z","msg":"咁多年仲講緊 好似冇嘢搵嘢講咁<br />\n講到尾得佢地兩個知心中有冇刺"},{"pid":"effb5c3d5e6f29af78324d45d3adcc8352aeccab","tid":2448674,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"baa1eaf8ad1aa0379520625e1b43f771bb26e28c","tid":2448674,"uid":339805,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:42:22.000Z","msg":"樓豬大劣人黎，係咁po大陸新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:43:10.000Z","msg":"吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4f5423486812f9e3bb5c2d8ac7cb04ed7677f2","tid":2448674,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:45:10.000Z","msg":"想屌Sandy <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aedd250f25f4a8845da1943fc2cfd907e3ea3246","tid":2448674,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:46:00.000Z","msg":"廢老不知足"},{"pid":"9c4d7a0f41c9295d4196b092a15250cbcc586515","tid":2448674,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af4f5423486812f9e3bb5c2d8ac7cb04ed7677f2","tid":2448674,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:45:10.000Z","msg":"想屌Sandy <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T06:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}